---
/* Diagnostics Section — Error Log grid */
---

<section class="mb-24" id="diagnostics">
  <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-8 reveal">
    <span class="label-mono text-accent-violet font-bold">0x01 // Error Log</span>
    <div class="h-px bg-dash-border flex-grow"></div>
  </div>
  <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-10 reveal delay-1">Tu reconnais cette situation ?</h2>
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-0 border-t border-l border-dash-border/40">

    <div class="p-8 border-r border-b border-dash-border/40 hover:bg-dash-surface/30 transition-colors reveal delay-1">
      <div class="label-mono text-accent-violet mb-4">Diagnostic #1</div>
      <p class="text-text-main font-medium leading-relaxed">Tu as suivi <span class="text-accent-violet">12 tutos YouTube</span> sur Make, n8n ou l'IA… mais tu ne sais toujours pas comment en vivre.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="p-8 border-r border-b border-dash-border/40 hover:bg-dash-surface/30 transition-colors reveal delay-2">
      <div class="label-mono text-accent-violet mb-4">Diagnostic #2</div>
      <p class="text-text-main font-medium leading-relaxed">Tu galères à te positionner. "Consultant automation" ? "Expert IA" ? Tu changes de bio LinkedIn <span class="text-accent-violet">toutes les semaines</span>.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="p-8 border-r border-b border-dash-border/40 hover:bg-dash-surface/30 transition-colors reveal delay-3">
      <div class="label-mono text-accent-violet mb-4">Diagnostic #3</div>
      <p class="text-text-main font-medium leading-relaxed">Le marché explose, mais tu restes au stade <span class="text-accent-violet">"side project"</span> pendant que les autres signent.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="p-8 border-r border-b border-dash-border/40 hover:bg-dash-surface/30 transition-colors reveal delay-4">
      <div class="label-mono text-accent-violet mb-4">Diagnostic #4</div>
      <p class="text-text-main font-medium leading-relaxed">Tu as peut-être même un CDI que tu veux quitter, mais tu ne sais pas par <span class="text-accent-violet">où commencer</span> pour te lancer.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="p-8 border-r border-b border-dash-border/40 hover:bg-dash-surface/30 transition-colors lg:col-span-2 reveal delay-5">
      <div class="label-mono text-accent-violet mb-4">Diagnostic #5</div>
      <p class="text-text-main font-medium leading-relaxed">Tu bosses seul, sans feedback, sans réseau, sans personne pour te dire si t'es sur la <span class="text-accent-violet">bonne voie</span>.</p>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
